{
  "stem": "5911.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My mother, luckily again, they opened a hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They made a hospital.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Within the ghetto, right away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had to-- to-- to-- there were sick people all over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you weren't-- you wore a-- a yellow star.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You weren't allowed out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only on work detail.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was terribly, terribly crowded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Terribly crowded.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I suppose now comes the story of the big action in October of 1941.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had to make place because we were terribly overcrowded.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "People were getting sick because it was very crowded.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they had an idea to get everybody out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said that it was census-taking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a-- a larger ghetto and a small ghetto, and they said that some people will be sent to the smaller ghetto to make more room and more food, because we were starving.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember my mother, again, my mother, covering her yellow star and going out with some of my clothes and bringing back food on the death-- under death of-- I mean, she would have been caught, she would have  been shot, nurse or no nurse.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember my father couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a softy like me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother did it a lot of times, not only this time, like, in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I had a lot of good clothes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she went, covered her Star of David, and went in to-- to exchange for food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no, no!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Left the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With whom should she trade in the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very, very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I suppose she did it during the night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Completely fenced in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only working detail left through the gates.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were-- there were guards all over, Lithuanians and Nazis, all over.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
